 \mathbb E(\max\{D_1,D_2\})=\int_0^v(1-\mathbb P(D\leqslant x)^2)\,\mathrm dx. 
 \mathbb P(D\leqslant x)=ax\mathbf 1_{0\lt x\lt u}+(1-b(v-x))\mathbf 1_{u\lt x\lt v}, 
